      "text": [
        "كُم الثَّقَلَيْنِ: كِتاب اللَّه وَعِتْرَتِي، وَلَنْ يَفتَرِقا حَتّى‏ يَرِدا عَلَي الحَوضَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.dr-ali-peiravi": [
          "31-259 According to the same documentation, on the authority of Ali (a.s.), the Prophet (S) said, “I leave two important things with you - God’s Book and my ‘Itra. They will not separate from each other until they return to me at the Pool.”"
        ]
      }
